#summary A Buddy list for sync
This is the default buddylist for jTorchat. If you are online often, then please add yourself here. Otherwise remove your entry (if already on the list). If you don't have access to edit this page write a comment and we will do it for you.

The jTorchat will use this URL https://jtorchat.googlecode.com/svn/wiki/Buddy_List.wiki
